===Most frequent venues===

The [[Shrine Auditorium]] has hosted the most Grammy Telecasts. Sixteen telecasts took place there between 1978 and 1999. It was the primary [[Los Angeles]] venue for the Grammy Awards from 1978 until the completion of the [[Staples Center]], which is where the Grammy Awards now take place.

